on social.

09:43.408 --> 09:44.888
You got four Sharks.
We love the deal.

09:44.932 --> 09:46.324
Everybody brings
something special.

09:46.368 --> 09:47.717
To go to 40%, we should put in
a little bit more money.

09:47.761 --> 09:49.066
Agreed.

09:49.110 --> 09:50.720
So that it should be 500K
at that point.

09:50.764 --> 09:51.939
Done.
Right?

09:51.982 --> 09:53.897
Now, look,
it seems like a lot,

09:53.941 --> 09:56.726
but, effectively, we're letting
you just stay creative

09:56.770 --> 09:59.120
and you guys will own
the majority still.

09:59.163 --> 10:02.558
But you've got four people
who touch every base,

10:02.602 --> 10:04.299
so that makes it a home run.

10:04.342 --> 10:05.517
We'd like to counter offer.

10:05.561 --> 10:08.738
- Can we talk for a second?
- Sure.

10:08.782 --> 10:10.348
If you guys don't mind,
- please?
- No, go ahead.

10:10.392 --> 10:12.699
Think about the amount of money
that you would have to pay

10:12.742 --> 10:15.179
to get four Sharks like us.

10:15.223 --> 10:16.833
You know,
the expertise that we bring

10:16.877 --> 10:18.530
is extreme in this case.

10:22.796 --> 10:25.929
Let's say $700,000.

10:25.973 --> 10:27.496
You do what you think is best.
Okay?

10:31.935 --> 10:35.722
So, I'm just going
to counter with this.

10:35.765 --> 10:39.247
Can we do $800,000,
40%?

10:42.990 --> 10:44.382
I think you might be
too greedy now.

10:44.426 --> 10:48.169
I think you've got a good deal
at $500,000 at 40%.

10:48.212 --> 10:50.998
O'If you give us the 40%,
we will blow this thing up,

10:51.041 --> 10:54.175
