of woe and misery for them.

11:04.751 --> 11:06.709
Alright,
you guys got a deal.

11:06.753 --> 11:07.710
Yeah!

11:07.754 --> 11:08.798
Good job.

11:08.842 --> 11:09.581
Good job, Peter.

11:09.625 --> 11:11.192
O'Fantastic.

11:11.235 --> 11:13.934
Oh, I thought you were
gonna lose that one.

11:13.977 --> 11:15.152
- I'm so excited for you.
- Thank you so much.

11:15.196 --> 11:16.937
That was
- really impressive.
- Thank you.

11:16.980 --> 11:18.547
Thank you.
