- Congratulations.

11:18.590 --> 11:19.722
- Well done.
- This is wonderful.

11:19.766 --> 11:21.115
- Alright!
- Thank you.

11:21.158 --> 11:23.900
Congratulations.
Well done!

11:23.944 --> 11:25.597
Thank you.

