11:42.832 --> 11:45.139
I come from
a really hardworking family,

11:45.182 --> 11:48.272
and I think that that's
an essence of my identity.

11:48.316 --> 11:50.753
I struggled at school.
I found it really difficult.

11:50.797 --> 11:53.408
My parents wanted me
to get a good education,

11:53.451 --> 11:55.192
go and get a nine-to-five job.

11:55.236 --> 11:56.672
There was always something
inside me, though,

11:56.716 --> 11:59.631
that wanted something different.

11:59.675 --> 12:02.460
I used to play a lot of tennis,
and at the age of 16,

12:02.504 --> 12:05.463
